annotationA: Uncharacterized protein NP15.6; It is involved in the biological process described with: respiratory electron transport chain
annotationB: NADH dehydrogenase (ubiquinone) 20 kDa subunit-like is a flavoprotein and iron-sulfur-containing oxidoreductase that catalyzes the oxidation of NADH to NAD. It is a component of the mitochondrial electron transport complex I, which is part of the oxidative phosphorylation pathway. It may have a role in regulating aggression behavior
